comment.author: 69859130@N05
comment._content: Gary - Even though Powerful Katrinka was assigned to the 13th Squadron initially, it ended up with either the 312th BG or 417th BG. Most of the early block A-20Gs that came to the 3rd Attack Group were dispersed to the other 2 Groups. The people posing aren't 3rd personnel. Sorry it has taken so long to get back to you. The San Diego Museum has quite an assortment of photos which have been identified by people that know far more than I do. The web site is really a place to bring as much information together and allow everyone a chance to see it. Gerry Kersey
